{"type": "article", "id": 27812, "title": "大理石花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-06T06:57:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021646079VE7bHe0ahCS4yDn.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你喜欢大理石花瓶，这个就像是“石中瓶”一定会让你眼前一亮。Svelata 系列由来自意大利的 <a href=\"http://www.morenoratti.com/\">Moreno Ratti</a> 设计，采用一整块 Carrara 大理石经过工匠手工雕刻而成，这也让每一款的造型都独一无二，看上去就像是从原石中开凿发现的宝藏。光滑的瓶体与凹凸不平的大理石形成了有趣的反差，既现代又透露出一股隽永的气质。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164605HRSTVWI2GEZBxkJ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164605wxEkosch3peWHmF8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164606DyRB7riaq41JPAOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164606t2q4m8ciB6rAWNaG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n\n"}